data.description: Move-in-ready and available now! Make your new home at the Colonies at McLean. This spacious, two-bedroom, two-full bath, north and east-facing corner unit features large double-hung windows, an expansive living and dining area, and a stylishly updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and recessed lighting. The king-sized primary bedroom aims to impress with a custom closet system and an ensuite bathroom with tiled walk-in shower with bench and LED backlit mirror. Abundant in-unit storage with built-in shelves in second bedroom and hall closets. Nest thermostat, electric heat pump, in-unit stacking washer and dryer. Elevator from covered parking and a variety of condominium amenities, including pool, tennis courts and club room, make for easy living at the Colonies. The condo association is pet-friendly and FHA and VA approved. The Colonies is close to shops, restaurants and services at Tysons Corner and has great access to transportation routes, local airports, and Tysons Corner Metro Station. Two-bedroom Model "A" floor plan can be found on the Colonies website. OFFER DEADLINE - Monday, April 15, 2024 at noon. Seller reserves the right to accept an offer prior to the deadline.
